üìò WORDPRESS LOCAL INSTALLATION (KALI LINUX + XAMPP)
-----------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ STEP 1 ‚Äî Start XAMPP Services
Start Apache + MySQL:
sudo /opt/lampp/lampp start

If MySQL already running ‚Üí OK.

-----------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ STEP 2 ‚Äî Create WordPress Database
1. Open browser:
   http://localhost/phpmyadmin

2. Click ‚ÄúNew‚Äù

3. Enter database name:
   wordpress

4. Click ‚ÄúCreate‚Äù

-----------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ STEP 3 ‚Äî Download & Move WordPress
1. Download WordPress:
cd /tmp
wget https://wordpress.org/latest.tar.gz

2. Extract:
tar -xvf latest.tar.gz

3. Move to XAMPP htdocs:
sudo mv wordpress /opt/lampp/htdocs/

4. (Optional) Rename folder:
sudo mv /opt/lampp/htdocs/wordpress /opt/lampp/htdocs/codexpro

-----------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ STEP 4 ‚Äî Configure wp-config.php
1. Go to folder:
cd /opt/lampp/htdocs/codexpro

2. Copy sample config:
sudo cp wp-config-sample.php wp-config.php

3. Edit file:
sudo nano wp-config.php

4. Set these values:

define( 'DB_NAME', 'wordpress' );
define( 'DB_USER', 'root' );
define( 'DB_PASSWORD', '' );
define( 'DB_HOST', 'localhost' );

5. Save:
CTRL + O ‚Üí Enter
CTRL + X

-----------------------------------------------------
‚úî You're now ready for WordPress installation:
Open: http://localhost/codexpro
